com.facebook.buck.android

Class AndroidResource

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.rules.AbstractBuildable
      • com.facebook.buck.android.AndroidResource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasAndroidResourceDeps, HasBuildTarget, AbiRule, Buildable, InitializableFromDisk<AndroidResource.BuildOutput>

    public class AndroidResource
extends AbstractBuildable
implements AbiRule, HasAndroidResourceDeps, InitializableFromDisk<AndroidResource.BuildOutput>
    An object that represents the resources of an android library.

    Suppose this were a rule defined in src/com/facebook/feed/BUILD: 

     android_resources(
   name = 'res',
   res = 'res',
   assets = 'buck-assets',
   deps = [
     '//first-party/orca/lib-ui:lib-ui',
   ],
 )
